# General configuraton for yt-dlp

## Include Subtitles

--embed-subs
--sub-langs "ja,zh,zh-CN,zh-Hans,en,de,fr"
--sub-format best

## Download-diirectory and filename

-o ~/Downloads/%(channel)s_%(playlist_title)s_%(title)s

## thumbnail

--embed-thumbnail

## Metadata

--embed-metadata

## Chapters

--embed-chapters

## Audio

--audio-multistreams
--audio-format opus
--audio-quality 0

## Video

--prefer-free-formats
--merge-output-format "mkv"

## Browser-Cookies

--cookies-from-browser firefox
